== Desirable features ========================================================
(without which the wiki is still manageable, but maybe less enjoyable)

                                                         p5w     |    p6w
-----------------------------------------------------------------+------------
* Contents (summarizing headings in the article). . not yet      |
                                                                 |
* Good merging when conflicts occur . . . . . . . . not yet      |
                                                                 |
* A plug-in system, so that formatting capabilities              |
  can be extended by the wiki owner . . . . . . . . not yet      |
                                                                 |
* RSS/Atom feeds                                                 |
** ...for site-wide recent changes. . . . . . . . . not yet      |
** ...for individual pages. . . . . . . . . . . . . not yet      |
** ...for a group of pages subscribed to by a user. not yet      |
